Nigerian singer and former member of the mo’hits crew, Wande Coal has finally reacted to his babymama’s allegation of son’s abduction. Few days ago, Wande Coal’s babymama, Temitope, stated that the singer gave his parents the child to take care of and she has always been denied the right to see the 10-year-old boy. Reacting to her accusations, Wande Coal released a statement saying everything his baby mama had said were all lies. Wande said that the only truth in her accusations was that she is the mother of his child and he happens to be the father. Read his statement below:-  The post Wande Coal Finally Reacts To Baby Mama’s Accusation Of Son’s Abduction appeared first on 360Nobs.com. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from 360Nobs.com. Click here to read the full text on the original website.